---
title: "How Feedback Loops in System Design Reinforce the Behaviors You Actually Want"
date: "2025-09-09"
summary: "Build feedback loops that reinforce desired behaviors. The right feedback at the right time shapes behavior more than any policy."
coverImage: ""
tags:
